latestIgtvVideos.title: Anisha Sethi X Tree of Life Resorts @treeofliferesortsandhotels
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We Traveled to Jaipur on A Much Awaited Getaway to @treeofliferesortsandhotels 
.

The Resort is 30 mins before Main Jaipur City and we took 3.5 hours to reach from New Delhi. 
No Covid Test was required to Travel to Jaipur.
.

We were really Happy with All Safety Measures taken by the resort, it’s a must visit during these times to do a quick short Luxurious Getaway.
:

With all Rooms Sanitized & Sealed before each guest Check - in. The Rooms are all spaced out and perfect for maintaining Social Distancing , you can have all meals in your rooms which was optional. Thanking the Hotel Staff for being so Cooperative and helpful.
.

Special Mention :The Pool Villas, Sunset Point, Aravali Rose Petals Bath, Authentic Rajasthani Food. 

My Beautiful Indian Ethnic Outfits are from @theloom.in ♥️

#anishasethixtreeofliferesorts #treeofliferesorts #muchneeded #getaway #poolvillas #jaipurdiaries #jaipurlove
